Package com.masri.TaskMangamentSystem.dao

Interface CrudDao<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The type of entity the DAO will manage.
All Known Implementing Classes:
ProjectDao, TaskDao, UserDao
public interface CrudDao<T>
A generic interface for CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations. This interface provides basic methods to be implemented by DAO classes for managing entities in the data store.
Author:
ahmad almasri
